  "markdown_content": "\n## Executive Summary\n\nUser requested creation of a valid JSON for an n8n workflow to automatically create courses in LearnWorlds. Manus successfully generated a comprehensive workflow package including validated JSON, documentation, and technical architecture. The workflow includes OAuth2 authentication, data validation, and error handling for robust API integration.\n\n\n## Context & Intent\n\nAutomate course creation process in LearnWorlds using n8n workflow automation platform\n\n\n## What Was Done\n\nCreated complete n8n workflow JSON with all necessary components for LearnWorlds API integration including authentication, validation, and error handling\n\n\n## Outputs Produced\n\n- [JSON] n8n Workflow — Validated workflow JSON for importing into n8n\n- [Documentation] Setup Guide — Complete instructions for workflow configuration and deployment\n- [Architecture] Technical Design — System design and integration architecture\n\n## Key Decisions & Validations\n\n- Used OAuth2 authentication for security\n- Implemented comprehensive error handling\n- Included data validation steps\n\n## Lessons Learned\n\nWorked well:\n\n- Structured workflow approach\n- Complete documentation package\nDiscoveries:\n\n- n8n workflow automation capabilities for e-learning platforms\n\n## Next Steps\n\n- Import workflow to n8n\n- Configure API credentials\n- Test course creation process\n---\nUID: MADY4tTOOO5H27YLFLFdd3 | Model: claude-sonnet-4-20250514 | Cost: $0.0098\n"
